find-idle-root-shells (0.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * Renames package.
  * Fixes is_valid_shell() check by fixing load_shells (found by Philipp Kern).
  * Turns off DRY_RUN mode. The script will now send SIGHUP signals to idle
    root processess started by non-adm group members.

