fsmi-root-protection (0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Ported to perl.
  * Scan processes' DISPLAY to identify utmp entries for xterminals.
  * Non adm users get stricter timing.
  * Non adm users get SIGHUPed after 30 minutes.
  * Adm members get de-escalated notifications ... hopefully decreases the
    flood of messages.

 -- Fabian Knittel <fabian.knittel@fsmi.uni-karlsruhe.de>  Tue, 16 Jan 2007 20:11:13 +0100

